high_descs: turn around and face the kitchen island
grab a fork off of the kitchen island counter
turn around and walk to the coffee maker on the kitchen counter left of the stove
place the fork inside a cup in the cabinet to the right of the dishwasher
pick up the cup with the fork in it
turn around to face the kitchen island again
place the cup down on the kitchen island counter top
anns.task_desc: place a cup with a fork in it down on the kitchen island counter

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the kitchen island.
Pick up the metal fork that is below the tomato on the kitchen island.
Turn left and walk over to where the coffee machine is on the counter.
Open the lower right cupboard door that is right in front of you and place the metal fork inside the glass that is in the cupboard.
Pick up the glass with the metal fork in it and close the cupboard door.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the kitchen island.
Place the glass with the metal fork in it onto the kitchen island.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a metal fork in it on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Turn around and face the green table.
Pick up the fork from the green table.
Turn left, then left again to face the green counter.
Open the cabinet on the right and put the fork in the glass inside the cabinet.
Take out the glass with the fork inside and close the cabinet.
Turn around and face the green table.
Put the glass with the fork inside on the green table.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a fork inside on a the green table.
